# Complete AZME→AZL ABA Integration Test
# Tests the full integration between AZME's high-level cognition and AZL's advanced ABA functions

say "🔌 Starting Complete AZME→AZL ABA Integration Test..."

# Initialize all AZME components with ABA integration
