# Test 3: FeedbackProcessor → AZL Advanced ABA Analysis
say "🔌 Step 4: Testing FeedbackProcessor → AZL Advanced ABA Analysis..."
emit "feedback.evaluate" with "learning_performance"
emit "action.completed" with "skill_practice"
emit "goal.completed" with "learning_goal"
